<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7157] Specify arbitrary config params outside of the component</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7157</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6365&quot; title=&quot;specify  appends, defaults, invariants outside of the component&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-6365&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-6365&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; added support for appends, defaults and invariants specified outside of the component via initParams.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be great if it would also be possible to configure arbitrary params via initParams.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Our use case is that we want to configure the &quot;healthcheckFile&quot; for the &quot;/admin/ping&quot; RequestHandler, so I&apos;d like to configure it like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  &amp;lt;initParams path=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/admin/ping&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;str name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;healthcheckFile&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;server-enabled.txt&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;/initParams&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
